#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:246
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings in the <guilabel>Identities</guilabel> page are fairly "
#| "straightforward. Select your default identity and click "
#| "<guibutton>Modify</guibutton>. Fill in the <guilabel>Your name</guilabel> "
